snippet.textDisplay:
"Désolé" (adjective) means, in case you do not know:
-Sorry (Je suis désolé de vouloir manger tes biscuits au cornichon)
-Desolate (Ce village est pire que tranquille, il est désolé!)
-Afraid (Not really used in a sentence)
-Disconsolate (Ma mère est présentement désolé en raison du récent divorce)
And other definitions related to sadness...

Also, "désolé" comes from the word "désolation", which can mean a profound sadness (emptiness), solitude and devastation.
Voilà, rien de compliqué, pas vrai?

I feel I have to write these things.
This band does not belong to any genre, on the contrary it's the band that possesses every genre whatever it is.
Every new song is actually "better" than the previous one, and even if there are still untouchable pieces, Gorillaz originality is perceivable every single time, they never get boring. And this leads me to think that their creativity is always alimented by themselves and all their collaborations.
I've always followed you, since I was nine, thank you Gorillaz.
